          </li>
          <li>
            <p>
              <m>\{\emptyset, \{a\}, \{a,b\}, \{a,c\}, \{a,b,c\}, X\}</m>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>
              <m>\{\emptyset, \{a\}, \{a,b\}, \{a,c\}, \{a,b,c\}, \{a,b,d\}, X\}</m>
