          <li>
            <p>
              The set <m>\{a,b\}</m> is a connected component of the topological space <m>X = \{a,b,c,d\}</m> with topology
              <me>
                \tau = \{\emptyset, \{a\}, \{a,b\}, \{c\}, \{d\}, \{c,d\}, \{a,c,d\}, \{a,c\}, \{a,d\}, \{a,b,c\}, \{a,b,d\}, X\}
